d developed by <a href=\"http://carolinethemes.com/\">Caroline Moore</a>, Ixion is a clean and professional theme geared to schools, non-profits, and organizations.</p>\n<p>Put your most exciting news front and center with a custom header image and a call-to-action button, highlight three noteworthy accomplishments on the homepage, and – with Jetpack&#8217;s Custom Content Types module &#8211; use <a href=\"https://en.support.wordpress.com/testimonials/\">Testimonials</a> to showcase your organization’s satisfied students or customers.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ixiondemo.wordpress.com/\">Visit the demo</a> or <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/ixion/\">take Ixion for a spin</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ixiondemo.wordpress.com/\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6781\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/03/22/introducing-ixion/ixion-ss/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=1403\" data-orig-size=\"1320,2205\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=1403?w=180\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=1403?w=613\" class=\"imgborder alignnone wp-image-6781 size-full\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=1403\" alt=\"Ixion screenshot\" width=\"840\" height=\"1403\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/ixion-ss.png?w=840&amp;h=1403 840w, https://themeshaper.files