";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:329:\"Now available through Jetpack, Content Options let users make small visual changes, like showing or hiding the author, date, featured images, and more.<img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6754&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Thomas Guillot\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17715:\"<p><a href=\"https://en.blog.wordpress.com/2016/08/30/introducing-content-options-an-easy-new-way-to-make-visual-changes-to-your-site/\">Last August</a>, we introduced a new WordPress.com Customizer panel called Content Options, which gives users an easy way to make small visual modifications across their sites – no custom CSS needed.</p>\n<p>Content Options supports four main features: <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5#blog-display\">Blog Display</a>, <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5#author-bio\">Author Bio</a>, <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5#post-details\">Post Details</a>, and <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5#featured-images\">Featured Images</a>.</p>\n<p>Content Options are now available to self-hosted WordPress sites with the latest version of <a href=\"https://jetpack.com/\">Jetpack</a> (4.5). Theme developers can add support for Content Options by following the <a href=\"https://jetpack.com/support/content-options/\">Jetpack guide</a>.</p>\n<p>Let&#8217;s look at the main features of Content Options in more detail.</p>\n<h2 id=\"blog-display\">Blog Display</h2>\n<p>Users can choose between displaying the full content of each post or an <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Excerpt\">excerpt</a> on the blog and category, tag, and date archive pages, as well as search results.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_6760\" style=\"max-width: 840px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6760\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/content-options-blog-display-full/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=840&#038;h=704\" data-orig-size=\"945,792\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=840&#038;h=704?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=840&#038;h=704?w=840\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6760\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=840&#038;h=704\" alt=\"Full post blog display option in Shoreditch\" width=\"840\" height=\"704\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=840&amp;h=704 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=150&amp;h=126 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=300&amp;h=251 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png?w=768&amp;h=644 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-full.png 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Full post blog display option in Shoreditch</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_6761\" style=\"max-width: 840px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6761\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/content-options-blog-display-excerpt/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=840&#038;h=294\" data-orig-size=\"953,334\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=840&#038;h=294?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=840&#038;h=294?w=840\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6761\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=840&#038;h=294\" alt=\"Post excerpt blog display option in Shoreditch\" width=\"840\" height=\"294\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=840&amp;h=294 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=150&amp;h=53 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=300&amp;h=105 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png?w=768&amp;h=269 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-excerpt.png 953w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Post excerpt blog display option in Shoreditch</figcaption></figure>\n<p><strong>Default Blog Display</strong></p>\n<p>If a theme displays either an excerpt or the full post depending on the post’s post format, theme developers can add a &#8220;Default&#8221; blog display option to let the theme keep its default blog display settings. For example, by default a theme might always displays posts with the Quote post format as the full post, so a quote is never truncated, while other post formats like Standard might be always displayed as an excerpt.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_6762\" style=\"max-width: 840px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6762\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/content-options-blog-display-default/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=840&#038;h=823\" data-orig-size=\"1204,1179\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=840&#038;h=823?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=840&#038;h=823?w=840\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6762\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=840&#038;h=823\" alt=\"Default blog display option in Button\" width=\"840\" height=\"823\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=840&amp;h=823 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=150&amp;h=147 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=300&amp;h=294 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=768&amp;h=752 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png?w=1024&amp;h=1003 1024w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/content-options-blog-display-default.png 1204w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Default blog display option in Button</figcaption></figure>\n<h2 id=\"author-bio\">Author Bio</h2>\n<p>On the single post view, users can opt to display the name and bio of the post&#8217;s author. This information comes directly from the author’s profile at Users <span class=\"st\">→</span> Your Profile, and their <a href=\"https://gravatar.com/\">Gravatar</a> image.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_6755\" style=\"max-width: 840px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6755\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/01/27/content-options-in-jetpack-4-5/con